These are total returns, though.

00:18:36.470 --> 00:18:39.290
These are what you
get as an investor.

00:18:39.290 --> 00:18:42.920
This is what you get if you
hold a particular security

00:18:42.920 --> 00:18:44.240
to maturity.

00:18:44.240 --> 00:18:49.130
Basically, on a given day,
you will get these spot rates.

