Here's another example
where you've now

00:58:35.130 --> 00:58:39.210
got some short positions
here, and the short positions

00:58:39.210 --> 00:58:40.920
are not from short selling.

00:58:40.920 --> 00:58:43.710
But the short positions
are in riskless bonds.

00:58:43.710 --> 00:58:47.320
In other words, now instead
of shorting a stock,

00:58:47.320 --> 00:58:50.860
you're shorting a bond or
selling a bond or borrowing

00:58:50.860 --> 00:58:54.770
money from a broker
and getting leverage.

00:58:54.770 --> 00:58:57.430
So this is leverage where
the security that you're

00:58:57.430 --> 00:59:01.150
